bsequent to central heating switching-off is examined. It is found that as\nthe heating power grows, the memory effect becomes increasingly important and\nit can greatly reduce the minimum ignition energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Feb 2021 16:41:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
