ential behavior of\n$\\mathbb{P}(\\lambda_1\\le \\sqrt{2(1-\\delta)\\log n})$ is also established.\n  As an immediate corollary, we get $\\lambda_1 \\approx \\sqrt{2 \\log n}$\ntypically, a result that surprisingly appears to be new. A key ingredient is an\nextremal spectral theory for weighted graphs obtained via the classical\nMotzkin-Straus theorem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Feb 2021 18:50:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
