ar effects exhibited by the system. Nonlinearity plays a\ncrucial role in controlling the ultrafast pulse propagation and could open a\nnew window for many nonlinear device applications. The findings of these new\noptical materials could possibly pave the way for promising applications in\nultrafast photonics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Feb 2021 13:11:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 05:40:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Jul 2021 18:40:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 15 Sep 2021 04:55:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-16"}
